data.description:
This cape cod is a great starter home for a single person or a small family! The neighborhood is absolutely beautiful and filled with the best people. With large bedrooms, a guest suite (bedroom and bathroom) in the basement, and a cozy breakfast nook, it is comfortable while retaining its original charm with original molding and hardwoods. 
The main heating and cooling system is an Eco friendly DUCTLESS MINI SPLIT in the family room, saving tons of money on electricity and offering a safer, more efficient option than baseboards and window air conditioners. The main bathroom was updated in 2021 with all new rustic hickory custom cabinetry, a deep soaking tub, and increased storage! Kitchen and bathroom floors are LifeProof and can stand up to water, kids, and pets easily. The back yard is a beautiful sanctuary with a brink patio, fire pit, and plenty of fenced in space for kids or pets to enjoy!
